SOURCE: https://github.com/emberjs/data/blob/main/packages/model/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import Model, { attr, belongsTo, hasMany } from '@ember-data/model';

export default class PersonModel extends Model {
