TITLE: Global Application Serializer for Null Properties
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of an application-wide serializer that restores the old behavior of setting missing properties to null
SOURCE: https://github.com/emberjs/data/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// app/serializers/application.js
// or App.ApplicationSerializer
export default DS.RESTSerializer.extend({
  normalize: function(type, hash, prop) {
    hash = this._super(type, hash, prop);
    type.eachAttribute(function(key) {
      if (!hash.hasOwnProperty(key)) {
        hash[key] = null;
      }
    }, this);
    return hash;
  },
});
```

