TITLE: Updating module hooks in @warp-drive/diagnostic
DESCRIPTION: Replace 'before' and 'after' hooks with 'beforeModule' and 'afterModule' in test modules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/emberjs/data/blob/main/packages/diagnostic/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
module('My Module', function(hooks) {
-  hooks.before(function(assert) {
+  hooks.beforeModule(function(assert) {
    // ...
  });

- hooks.after(function(assert) {
+ hooks.afterModule(function(assert) {
    // ...
  });
});
```

